TextEng: I suppose that makes you a burglar of some sort? Come to rob me, have you?
Text: 그럼 좀도둑쯤 되시나? 나를 털러 온 건가?

TextEng: Back again, are you? Something you need?
Text: 또 왔군? 필요한 게 있나?

TextEng: Fare you well, <sir/madam>.
Text: 안녕히 가시오, 선생.

TextEng: I'm sure you know the way out.
Text: 나가는 길은 알겠죠.

TextEng: Yes, leave me be.
Text: 그래, 이만 가 주시오.

TextEng: Ah. This should be interesting.
Text: 아. 재미있겠군.

TextEng: Oh, I suppose there's no harm. I haven't seen a soul for days with all that's going on.
Text: 오, 그러지. 요즘 꼴이 이렇다 보니 며칠째 사람 구경도 못했거든.

TextEng: Well... it's not like you have the plague or anything. Go on, then.
Text: 음... 역병 환자는 아니잖아. 그럼 말해 보게.

TextEng: Oh, all right. (sigh) It's not like there's much else going on, with the plague and all.
Text: 아, 알겠다. (한숨) 역병 때문에 할 일도 별로 없으니까.

TextEng: Merciful heavens, no. Well... there are the creatures at the zoo, of course. They have all been there since before the plague, however.
Text: 세상에, 아니야. 음... 동물원에 있는 생명체들이 있긴 하지. 하지만 역병 전부터 있던 것들이야.

TextEng: Nothing that you wouldn't have heard elsewhere, <sir/madam>. To be honest, what little chat I've had with the neighbours has been about anything *but* the plague.
Text: 다른 데서도 들었을 법한 얘기뿐이야, 선생. 솔직히 이웃들과 떠든 것도 죄다 역병 말고 다른 얘기였지.

TextEng: We nobles have been keeping to ourselves, mostly, but I do try to keep up on the latest gossip, if that's what you mean.
Text: 요즘 귀족들은 대체로 문 걸어 잠그고 지내지만, 소문은 챙겨 듣는 편이지. 그 말씀이라면.

TextEng: Well... there is the business with Meldanen. But talking about him is never a good idea.
Text: 음... 멜다넨 얘기가 있긴 한데, 그 사람 이야기는 하는 게 좋아 보이지 않군.

TextEng: Well, that girl Formosa is looking for people who will listen to her. She's down in the southeast square trying to stir up folks against Meldanen.
Text: 그 포르모사라는 아가씨가 자기 말을 들어줄 사람을 찾고 있어. 남동쪽 광장에서 멜다넨을 못마땅해하며 사람들을 부추기고 있지.

TextEng: I don't know. That tavern, the Board Laid Bare? It has quite a scandalous reputation, I hear.
Text: 모르겠군. 그 선술집, 적나라한 게시판 말인가? 꽤 선정적이라는 소문이 돌지.

TextEng: I'm looking for a housekeeper. Mine died of the plague, I hear. No good?
Text: 난 집사를 구하는 중이야. 내 사람은 역병으로 죽었다더군. 관심 없나?

TextEng: Is there something else you wanted to know?
Text: 다른 게 더 궁금한가?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Success]</Start> I suppose there's no way for the wizard to know, is there? Well... word is that Meldanen recently accquired a young woman for his amusement.
Text: <StartCheck>[성공]</Start> 그 마법사가 알아챌 방법은 없겠지, 아마? ...그래, 들리는 말로는 멜다넨이 최근 재미를 보려고 젊은 여자를 들였대.

TextEng: He won't let her out, and the rumors say that she's rather strange... perhaps not quite human. The gods only know what he wants with her. Rather sordid business, no?
Text: 밖엔 못 나가게 하고, 소문으로는 조금 특이한 아가씨라던데... 완전히 인간은 아닐지도. 도대체 뭘 하려는 건지, 신들만 아실 일이지. 꽤 추잡하지, 안 그런가?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Failure]</Start> It would do more harm than you know. Meldanen's a fearsome man... I wouldn't mind if he turned up dead one day, myself.
Text: <StartCheck>[실패]</Start> 자네가 생각하는 것보다 더 큰 화를 부를 거야. 멜다넨은 무서운 사람이지... 언젠가 시체로만 나타난다면야 나도 불만은 없겠지만.

TextEng: Not that I've heard. Mind you, we nobles have been keeping to ourselves, lately. The zoo's in the northeast if you want to see for yourself.
Text: 내가 듣기론 없어. 뭐, 요즘은 다들 문 닫고 지내니까. 직접 보고 싶으면 북동쪽 동물원으로 가 보게.

TextEng: Is there something else you need, then?
Text: 그럼 또 필요한 게 있나?

TextEng: Err... perhaps, I don't know. Sureshot... or, that is, Lord Montgomery... is in charge of the zoo and I haven't heard a peep from him since the whole plague business began.
Text: 글쎄... 잘 모르겠네. 백발백중, 그러니까 몽고메리 경이 동물원을 맡고 있는데, 역병 난 뒤로는 소식이 뚝이야.

TextEng: Perhaps you might want to speak to him. The zoo's in the northeast part of the district if you haven't already been.
Text: 가 봐서 직접 얘기해 보게. 동물원은 지구 북동쪽에 있어.

TextEng: I am no expert on the plague, <sir/madam>. There is no plague in Blacklake, after all. But I will answer what I can.
Text: 난 역병 전문가는 아냐, 선생. 검은호수엔 역병도 없고. 그래도 아는 선에서 답해 보지.

TextEng: What were you looking for, then?
Text: 그래서, 뭘 찾으시는 건가?

TextEng: I can show you the way out. (sigh) Oh, go ahead.
Text: 나가는 길을 알려 줄 수는 있어. (한숨) 자, 말해 보게.

TextEng: What do you want to know?
Text: 무엇을 알고 싶지?

TextEng: That much is obvious.
Text: 그 정도는 뻔하지.

TextEng: Hmph. Angling for an invitation, are we? Well you can't stay here. The Board Laid Bare by the south gate is the nearest place.
Text: 흠. 초대라도 바라는 건가? 여기서는 못 묵어. 남문 근처의 적나라한 게시판 선술집이 제일 가깝네.

TextEng: I'm afraid there isn't one in the area. We were trying to raise coin for a temple devoted to Sune... but I'm sure you're not interested in that.
Text: 안타깝지만 이 근처엔 그런 곳이 없어. 수네의 신전을 세우려고 모금을 하긴 했는데... 자네가 관심 있을 리는 없겠지.

TextEng: No. But you can buy equipment at the Board Laid Bare, I hear. It's by the south gate.
Text: 아니. 대신 적나라한 게시판 선술집에서 장비를 판다고 들었네. 남문 근처야.

TextEng: Is there something else?
Text: 또?

TextEng: Why have you intruded? Get out! Out! Evil dog!
Text: 왜 침입했나? 당장 나가! 나가! 못된 개 같은 것!

TextEng: Not one step closer or I shall scream! Why have you invaded my home?!
Text: 한 발짝만 더 오면 비명을 지를 거야! 왜 내 집을 침범한 거지?!

TextEng: What is this? Has the city fallen apart, now? Get out of here this instant!
Text: 이게 뭐야? 도시가 완전히 무너진 건가? 당장 나가! 어서!

TextEng: Get out of my home! Thief! Vagrant! Where is the watch when you need them?!
Text: 내 집에서 나가! 도둑! 부랑자! 경비대는 대체 어디 있는 거야!

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Success]</Start> I... suppose you can be trusted. A woman on her own in these dangerous times has to be cautious, you understand.
Text: <StartCheck>[성공]</Start> 알겠네... 믿어도 되겠지. 이런 험한 때에 여자가 혼자면 조심해야 하잖나, 이해해.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Failure]</Start> I don't trust the look of you! Get out this instant!!
Text: <StartCheck>[실패]</Start> 꼴이 영 못 미더워! 당장 나가!

TextEng: Get out, before I call the watch on you!
Text: 경비대를 부르기 전에 나가!

TextEng: What was it you wanted, then, <sir/madam>?
Text: 그래서, 뭘 원했지, 선생?

TextEng: Around *here*? Oh... you mean around the district.
Text: '여기'라니... 아, 이 지구 얘기인가?

TextEng: It was bound to happen. (sigh)
Text: 결국 이럴 줄 알았지. (한숨)

TextEng: At any rate, if you want you can see for yourself. Meldanen's estate is in the northwest. I wouldn't advise going there, though... he won't see you.
Text: 어쨌든 직접 확인하고 싶으면 북서쪽의 멜다넨 저택으로 가 보게. 추천하진 않아... 만나 주지도 않을 테니까.

TextEng: I never said that, however. His mansion is in the northwest part of the district... but I'd avoid it like the plague.
Text: 다만, 내가 가 보라고 한 건 아냐. 저택은 지구 북서쪽... 난 역병처럼 피하고 싶군.

TextEng: We'd all like to see the wizard gone, but what are *we* supposed to do about it? Perhaps you'd like to help her, I don't know.
Text: 다들 그 마법사가 사라졌으면 하긴 하지만, 우리가 뭘 할 수 있겠나? 그녀를 돕고 싶은 거라면... 글쎄, 자네 마음이지.

TextEng: Disgruntled Woman
Text: 불만 가득한 여성

TextEng: I... I can't fight you. Take what I have and go. Just go.
Text: 싸울 수 없어. 가진 걸 가져가고 가. 제발.

TextEng: Don't... don't let me see you here again... please.
Text: 다시는... 다시는 여기서 마주치지 않게 해... 제발.

TextEng: I'm sorry to disappoint you, but if you are here to rob me you are too late. I've nothing left. If you have other business, state it and get out.
Text: 기대 깨서 미안하지만, 털러 왔다면 늦었어. 남은 건 없어. 다른 용무가 있으면 말하고 나가.

TextEng: I'm not interested in donating today, thank you.
Text: 기부는 사양하겠네, 오늘은.

TextEng: Very well. I'm not sure what you were getting at, but I'm glad you are leaving.
Text: 좋아. 무슨 속셈인지는 모르겠지만 떠난다니 다행이군.

TextEng: Very well... but make it quick. I'm not sure what you are up to...
Text: 좋아... 하지만 빨리 해. 뭘 꾸미는지 모르겠네...

TextEng: Ah, I see. Well, it appears I have very little choice. Take what you must. Just get the hell out afterward.
Text: 아, 알겠어. 선택지가 별로 없나 보군. 필요한 만큼 가져가. 대신 곧장 꺼져.

TextEng: Hold on. If you are trying to find out if I have gold to steal, the answer is no, I don't. Someone beat you to it, so state whatever other business you have and get out.
Text: 잠깐. 훔칠 금이 있는지 떠보는 거라면, 없어. 이미 누가 훔쳐 갔거든. 그러니 다른 볼일이 있으면 말하고 나가.

TextEng: There was something about a woman named Formosa, but whatever business she had seems to be concluded. This district is quite quiet now.
Text: 포르모사라는 여인 얘기가 있긴 했는데, 무슨 일이었든 끝난 모양이야. 지금은 꽤 조용하지.

TextEng: If it's all the same, I don't want to spend much time in your... charming presense. Besides, Meldanen is a fearsome man. Myself, I wouldn't mind if he turned up dead one day.
Text: 실례지만, 자네의... 매혹적인 '존재감' 옆에 오래 있고 싶진 않네. 게다가 멜다넨은 무서운 사람이라서. 개인적으론 언젠가 죽은 채로만 나타나면 좋겠지만.

TextEng: Ooh, aren't you a charmer. I suppose there's no harm in a friendly... chat. Well... word is that Meldanen recently accquired a young woman for his amusement.
Text: 어이쿠, 말은 참 잘하는군. 잠깐 수다 떠는 건 괜찮겠지. 그러니까... 들리는 말로는 멜다넨이 최근 재미를 보려고 젊은 여자를 들였대.

TextEng: No, not really. There was some trouble with a mage named Meldanen, but that is long over with. This district is pretty quiet now.
Text: 아니, 딱히. 멜다넨이라는 마법사 때문에 소란이 좀 있었을 뿐이고, 그것도 진작 끝났어. 지금은 꽤 조용한 편이지.

TextEng: You were not invited. Get out!
Text: 자네는 초대받지 못했어. 나가!
